==反应机理==
反应[[催化循环|催化循环]]经过[[氧化加成|氧化加成]]、[[转金属|转金属]]、[[顺反异构化|顺反异构化]]和[[还原消除|还原消除]]几步，见 [https://www.organic-chemistry.org/namedreactions/hiyama-coupling.shtm 此图] {{Wayback|url=https://www.organic-chemistry.org/namedreactions/hiyama-coupling.shtm |date=20200109050919 }}。其中关键是用氟离子把有机硅中低极化的 Si–R 键活化，以便进行金属交换。

==拓展==
1、用末[[炔|炔]]与[[四甲基二硅氧烷|四甲基二硅氧烷]]<ref>Scott E. Denmark and Zhigang Wang, "[http://www.orgsynth.org/orgsyn/pdfs/v81p0054.pdf Platinum Catalyzed Hydrosilylation and Palladium Catalyzed Cross-coupling: One-pot Hydroarylation of 1-Heptyne to (''E'')-1-(1-Heptenyl)-4-Methoxybenzene] {{Wayback|url=http://www.orgsynth.org/orgsyn/pdfs/v81p0054.pdf |date=20071008035054 }}", ''[[Organic_Syntheses|Organic Syntheses]]'', ''Vol.'' '''81''', p.54 (2005).</ref> 或[[六甲基环三硅氧烷|六甲基环三硅氧烷]]<ref>Scott E. Denmark and Zhigang Wang, "[http://www.orgsynth.org/orgsyn/pdfs/v81p0042.pdf Palladium Catalyzed Cross-coupling of (''Z'')-1-Heptenyldimethylsilanol with 4-Iodoanisole: (''Z'')-(1-Heptenyl)-4-methoxybenzene] {{Wayback|url=http://www.orgsynth.org/orgsyn/pdfs/v81p0042.pdf |date=20071010061507 }}", ''[[Organic_Syntheses|Organic Syntheses]]'', ''Vol.'' '''81''', p.42 (2005).</ref>[[原位|原位]]生成烯基卤进行反应。

2、[[氯化镍|氯化镍]]、[[LiHMDS|LiHMDS]]和[[去甲麻黄碱|去甲麻黄碱]]存在下，以[[氟化铯|氟化铯]]作氟离子源，仲卤代烃与有机硅之间的偶联：<ref>{{cite journal en|title=Hiyama Reactions of Activated and Unactivated Secondary Alkyl Halides Catalyzed by a Nickel/Norephedrine Complex|author=Neil A. Strotman, Stefan Sommer, and Gregory C. Fu|journal=[[Angew._Chem._Int._Ed.|Angew. Chem. Int. Ed.]]|year=2007|volume=46|pages=3556–3558|doi=10.1002/anie.200700440}}</ref>

